Title: The Break Up
Plot: At the urging of everyone, Liz finally breaks up with her beeper salesman boyfriend, but the path back to "single and loving it" proves to be filled with unforeseen obstacles.
GuestStars: Dean Winters, Rachel Dratch, Chris Hansen, Devin Richards, Maulik Pancholy, Katrina Bowden, Keith Powell, Lonny Ross, Stan Tracy, Henry Boyle
